text: Cockneys vs Zombies is a British zombie apocalypse-comedy film produced by Limelight Molinare and co-Director Matthias Hoene starring Harry Treadaway, Rasmus Hardiker, Michelle Ryan, Georgia King, Richard Briers, Honor Blackman and Alan Ford. ==Cast== *Rasmus Hardiker as Terry *Harry Treadaway as Andy *Michelle Ryan as Katy *Alan Ford as Ray *Georgia King as Emma *Jack Doolan as Davey Tuppence *Ashley Thomas as Mental Mickey *Tony Gardner as Clive *Tony Selby as Daryl *Georgina Hale as Doreen *Dudley Sutton as Eric *Richard Briers as Hamish *Honor Blackman as Peggy *Elizabeth Webster as Natasha ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2012 comedy movies Category:Zombie movies Category:2012 horror movies Category:British comedy movies Category:Horror thriller movies Category:2010s English-language movies Category:Apocalyptic movies Category:Movies set in London
